{
  "scripts": {
    "http://localhost:5173/#/short-video/auth": "auth.js",
    "https://creator.douyin.com/*": ["common.js", "douyin-creator.js"],
    "https://lf-zt.douyin.com/*": ["common.js", "douyin-creator.js"],
    "https://creator.xiaohongshu.com/new/home": ["common.js", "xiaohongshu-creator.js"],
    "https://channels.weixin.qq.com/platform/": ["common.js", "shipinhao-creator.js"],
    "https://baijiahao.baidu.com/builder/rc/home": ["common.js", "baijiahao-creator.js"],
    "https://baijiahao.baidu.com/": ["common.js", "baijiahao-creator.js"],
    "https://apidev.china9.cn/api/mediaauth/*": ["kuaishou-creator.js"]
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "common.js": "公共工具库，包含消息发送、DOM 操作等通用函数"
  },
  "注释": [
    "在这里配置 URL 和对应的脚本文件",
    "URL 支持通配符 * 匹配任意字符",
    "例如: https://www.douyin.com/* 匹配所有抖音页面",
    "或精确匹配: http://localhost:5173/#/short-video/auth",
    "",
    "脚本支持两种格式：",
    "1. 单个脚本：\"URL\": \"script.js\"",
    "2. 多个脚本（依赖注入）：\"URL\": [\"dependency.js\", \"main.js\"]",
    "   数组中的脚本会按顺序注入，前面的脚本可以被后面的脚本使用",
    "",
    "脚本文件放在同一目录下",
    "支持相对路径",
    "修改后需要重启应用才能生效"
  ]
}
